I love the idea of bitcoin, although I'd personally never even think of 'investing' in it like others are doing. That's just gambling, in my opinion. Rainy day money? Sure, that's a better idea..
&nbsp;
At the end of the day, however.. the only real currency is the sum of the world's available resources. The matter and energy that goes into producing the things that money buys.
